<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="3779912" n="1"/> 
  <opener></opener>
  <opener><salute><choice><abbr>V.</abbr><expan>Viro</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Acu.</abbr><expan>Acutissimo</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Celeb.</abbr><expan>Celeberrimo</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">I. Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o</rs>, <abbr>Prof.</abbr> <abbr>Geom.</abbr> <choice><abbr>Dign.</abbr><expan>Dignissimo</expan></choice> Amico <choice><abbr>Honor.</abbr><expan>Honoratissimo</expan></choice> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102039186">I. L. F.</rs> <choice><abbr>S.</abbr><expan>Salutat</expan></choice><supplied>,</supplied> Patavium.</salute></opener>
  <p><lb/>Quant<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <unclear reason="illegible">l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titia</unclear> perfus<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> fuerim, acceptis <rs type="letter">Literis</rs> Tuis <abbr>Humaniss.</abbr> verbis exprimere me fateor nequaqu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/>posse. Extab<choice><orig><g ref="#an">ā</g></orig><reg>an</reg></choice>t in illis expressissima amoris Tui at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> candoris <foreign xml:lang="grc">τεκμήρια</foreign><note type="editorial">"extabant expressissima… τεκμήρια" = "es zeigten sich die deutlichsten Beweise…".</note> nulla simulata affectationi imitanda.
    <lb/>Extabant plurima ad Rem <abbr>p.</abbr> <abbr>Liter.</abbr> spectantia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> rescire talium rerum Curiosum neminem pigeat, extabat deni<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
    <lb/>(quod primo loco fuisset memorand<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>) appuls<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> tui tam felicis tam exoptati ad ill<choice><orig><g ref="#aacut">á</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m musar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sedem Patavi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>mihi gratissima significatio. Faxit <abbr>D. O. M.</abbr> ut per Te <seg type="transposition">porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> cresc<choice><orig><g ref="#an">ā</g></orig><reg>an</reg></choice>t</seg> <abbr>nobiliss.</abbr> <abbr>Scient.</abbr> <abbr>Mathemat.</abbr> illustre<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>
    <lb/>gloria <rs type="organisation">L<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>cei Patavini</rs>, quod Te habet, et <rs type="organisation"><abbr>Basil.</abbr></rs> quod Te brevi habiturum l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ti ominamur, promoveatur<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Ipsi<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> Res, ad
    <lb/>consideration<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> magnali<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> suor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in hoc stupendo mundi <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dificio elucescenti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, nos vocantis honos. Nunc<supplied>,</supplied> <choice><abbr>Am.</abbr><expan>Amicissime</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>V.</abbr><reg>Vir</reg></choice><supplied>,</supplied> ut
    <lb/>videas confidenti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> me<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, <unclear><gap/></unclear> quod Te, c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> vix pedem in Terram illam intuleris etiam at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> rogo. Nosti apud
    <lb/>Vos <rs type="place">Patavii</rs> t<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>pis ante a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>os aliquot excusum esse nitidissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ill<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Alcoran<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Arabico<supplied>-</supplied>lat. cum Prodromo oper<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
    <lb/><abbr>Doct.</abbr> Maraccii<!-- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ludovico_Marracci 2. Bände Patavii 1698 ...Ludovico Marraccio... -->. Hujus <unclear>2<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice></unclear> exemplaria cum in aliis <abbr>regionib.</abbr> sint satis rara et cara, <rs type="person">amici no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ulli</rs> ex
    <lb/><rs type="place">Belgio</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me peti<choice><orig><g ref="#ehat">ê</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>re ut si poss<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> duo saltem exemplaria ipsis procurar<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>. Quib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> c<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> lubenter mor<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
    <lb/>gererem, Te <abbr>Hum.</abbr> <abbr>V.</abbr> compellare audeo, ut nisi grave sit, et cum vacabit, bina exemplaria integra
    <lb/>emere, huic<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs type="person">mercatori</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo Liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tibi transmitten<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, tradere velis. Precium solvet indicat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, hic
    <lb/><rs type="person">mercator</rs>, aut si mavis, <abbr>Hon.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Parenti</rs> Tuo hic ego solv<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>. Cum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> in ea nunc degas Regione, ubi multa
    <lb/>aliquando Rabbinica et Orientalia in lucem prodiere, scire gestir<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, n<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m non in Bibliopoliis talium
    <lb/>sat vilis a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ona sit, at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> inprimis n<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m et quo pretio veneant <hi rend="u"><rs type="person">Bartoloccii</rs> <rs type="biblio">Bibliot. Rabbin.</rs></hi><supplied>,</supplied> <hi rend="u">Abarbanelis<!-- https://archive.org/details/bub_gb_RdTiILPvUBgC/page/n5/mode/2up -->
    <lb/><rs type="biblio">Co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ent. Hebr. in Pentateuch</rs></hi>. Quid, inquis, frontem ne plane perfricuisti, me<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Tuis <unclear><gap/></unclear><!-- evtl. varis unius vanis --> usib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> patere
    <lb/>arbitraris? Culp<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> fateor: <abbr>Am.</abbr> <abbr>V.</abbr> et nisi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sidi<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> sit in benignitate tua at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> sincera amicitia
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> illibat<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> mihi servare digneris eous<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> impudent<unclear>iam</unclear> progredi <choice><abbr>n.</abbr><expan>non</expan></choice> aus<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> essem. <choice><orig>adder<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></orig><reg>Adderem</reg></choice> no<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>ulla
    <lb/>nova de vacantib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> officiis <abbr>Eccles.</abbr> ambienti<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Persona, machinationib<choice><orig><g ref="#us">[us]</g></orig><reg>us</reg></choice> et sic obtinendis
    <lb/><abbr>it.</abbr> magis remota de tragica fortuna <abbr>Cel.</abbr> <abbr>Mat.</abbr> de <rs type="person">Façio</rs> <abbr>etc.</abbr> nisi h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c et plura alia
    <lb/>ob aliis pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipu<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> <abbr>Amic.</abbr> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> utri<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Bringolfio</rs> pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cepta mihi esse <unclear>scire</unclear> suspicarer.
    <lb/>Vale <abbr>Clar.</abbr> Vir et ubicun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> mea opella sive <unclear>hic</unclear> sive <unclear>dil...</unclear>
    <lb/>possis <unclear>s?</unclear> <unclear>proficu?</unclear>, <unclear>e</unclear><choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice><!-- oder i<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> --> parat<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> <unclear>p</unclear>er <unclear><gap/></unclear>xp<unclear><gap/></unclear>ta.</p>
  <closer>
    <lb/><dateline><rs type="place">Basil.</rs> <date>15. <abbr>Cal.</abbr> Mart.</date> die ante Iejuni<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></dateline>
    <lb/>public<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> in <abbr>Reform.</abbr> <abbr>Helv.</abbr> ob Pac<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> restitut<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
    <lb/>indictum.</closer>
    <postscript><p><lb/>Plurima salute Te
    <lb/>impertiat <rs type="person"><abbr>Th.</abbr> Bury</rs><!-- Theodor Burckhardt 1682-08-15 gest. 1759-11-21 ab 1708 Pfarrer zu St. Jakob, 1716-1759 Helfer zu St. Peter -->
    <lb/>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>unis amicus<supplied>.</supplied></p></postscript>
    <closer>    
